Privacy Policy for yt2summary Chrome Extension
Effective Date: 21/07/2025

Thank you for using yt2summary! This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use the yt2summary Chrome Extension ("Extension").

1. Information We Collect
We collect the following types of information:

a. Email Address
Collected during login or account creation.

Used to authenticate users and manage user sessions.

b. IP Address
Automatically collected upon use.

Used for rate limiting, fraud prevention, and maintaining service integrity.

c. Payment Information
If you initiate a transaction, we may collect billing details through a secure, third-party payment processor.

We do not store raw payment card information ourselves.

2. How We Use Your Information
We use your information solely for the purpose of providing and improving the Extension:

Authenticate and manage user accounts.

Monitor usage for fair access and security (via rate limiting).

Process payments and manage subscriptions.

Communicate with you regarding account or service issues.

3. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not sell or rent your personal information.

We may share your information only under these circumstances:

Legal Requirements: To comply with law enforcement or legal obligations.

Service Providers: With trusted vendors (e.g., cloud hosting, payment processors) who perform services on our behalf and under confidentiality agreements.

4. Data Retention
Email and IP addresses are retained for the duration of your account.

Payment-related records are retained as required by financial regulations.

5. Data Security
We implement industry-standard measures to protect your data:

HTTPS encryption for all communications.

Secure session and credential management.

PCI-compliant payment processing via third-party services.

6. Your Rights
You have the right to:

Access or update your personal information.

Request deletion of your account and associated data.

Contact us with any privacy-related concerns.

To exercise these rights, please email us at n.cirit.n@gmail.com.

7. Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy occasionally. Significant changes will be communicated via the Extension or email.

Last Updated: 21/07/2025

8. Contact Us
If you have questions or concerns, contact us at:

Email: n.cirit.n@gmail.com


